"Le frontend est codé en `Svelte <https://svelte.dev/>`_. Il est en charge"
" du rendu de l'interface graphique et du board de Backgammon."
msgstr ""
"The frontend is coded in `Svelte <https://svelte.dev/>`_. It is "
"responsible for rendering the graphical interface and the Backgammon "
"board."

#: ../../source/faq.rst:170
msgid ""
"L'application est encapsulée avec `Wails <https://wails.io/>`_, "
"permettant la production d'applications Desktop natives, déclinables sous"
" Windows et Linux."
msgstr ""
"The application is encapsulated with `Wails <https://wails.io/>`_, "
"enabling the production of native desktop applications that can run on "
"both Windows and Linux."

#: ../../source/faq.rst:173
msgid "La base de données est gérée par `Sqlite <https://www.sqlite.org/>`_."
msgstr "The database is managed by `SQLite <https://www.sqlite.org/>`_."

